outputs.output_descr:
CPAP Outcome 5:  Rights upheld and protected through accountable, accessible and equitable Rule of Law institutions.

Project Outputs as per AWP:-
Output 1: UNDP Rule of Law Programme in Darfur managed according to UNDP requirements;
Output 2: Human rights awareness enhanced;
Output 3: Local communities empowered and access to justice improved;
Output 4: Enhance dialogue among Darfurian Stakeholders and increase access to national and international legal resources;
Output 5: State Government  Rule of Law Institutions strengthened to provide rule of law services to Darfuri population;
